Sankhani khungu loyendetsa kuti muphunzire
1. Mtundu uyenera kufanana ndi zinthu zamkati.
Posankha khungu, ndibwino kuti mumvetsere mtundu wa mipando ina mu phunziroli, makamaka mtundu wa kabukuka. Mipando yamakono ndiyofunika kwambiri pakugwirizana. Posankha mtundu wakhungu, ngati titayang'ana mtundu wa mipando. gwirizanitsani ndi mipando, phunziroli limatha kumangidwa bwino.
2. Makina owala bwino azikhala bwino.
Ndi bwino kusankha mtundu wopepuka wa khungu lophunzirira, chifukwa utoto wowala u
... (231 chars skipped) ... 
idwa bwino.
3. Sankhani mitundu yatsopano.
Yesetsani kupewa mitundu yapamwamba yophunzirira khungu. Mitundu yokongola kwambiri imapangitsa ogwiritsa ntchito kukhala otopetsa komanso osathandiza pophunzira ndi kugwira ntchito. Chifukwa chake, khungu labwino kwambiri ndikusankha mtundu watsopano, monga buluu ndi zoyera. Zonsezi zidzakhalanso bwino.
Mokhwima ulamuliro khalidwe kuonetsetsa kuti nsalu mlingo magwiritsidwe ndi wamkulu kuposa 95%.

... (231 chars skipped) ...
itsanzo zaulere zokhala ndi mitundu yopitilira 650 ya nsalu zokumana ndi zosowa zamsika.

Chengdu SANKE industry Co, Ltd ("SK") ndi odziwika bwino opanga makina opanga ma confectionery ku China.SK ndi katswiri pakupanga ndi kupanga makina oyikamo komanso mizere yopangira maswiti.
SK idakhazikitsidwa mu 1999 ndi Bambo Du Guoxian, patatha zaka 20 zachitukuko SK inali ndi zilembo 98 zaku China zovomerezeka, zidapanga makina masauzande ambiri ndikugulitsa mayiko ndi madera a 48.SK inali ndi mafakitale awiri omwe anali R&D Center ndi Assembly Factory.

Chophatikizika ndi kuphatikiza kwa zinthu ziwiri kapena zingapo zachilengedwe kapena zopanga zokhala ndi zinthu zosiyanasiyana zakuthupi ndi zamankhwala.Kuphatikizikako kumapangitsa kuti zinthu zapansi zikhale bwino, monga mphamvu zowonjezera, zogwira mtima kapena zolimba.Zida zophatikizika ndi nsalu zaukadaulo zimagwira ntchito nthawi zambiri.Chifukwa cha ubwino wawo wosiyana ndi zipangizo zamakono, zipangizo zamakono ndi nsalu zamakono zimagwiritsidwa ntchito kwambiri m'mafakitale osiyanasiyana monga zamlengalenga, zomangamanga, magalimoto, mankhwala, asilikali ndi masewera.
TheMakina odulira laser a CO2yopangidwa ndi Golden Laser ndi chida chamakono chomwe chimatha kudula masanjidwe ovuta kwambiri kuchokera ku nsalu molondola komanso moyenera.Ndi makina athu odulira laser, kudula nsalu kapena thovu mumakampani opanga zinthu kumakhala kotsika mtengo.
Kupanga nsalu zapamwamba komanso zotsika kumatha kupangidwa kuchokera ku ulusi wochita kupanga monga (nsalu zolukidwa, zoluka kapena zoluka) komanso nsalu zaukadaulo zaukadaulo monga zida zophatikizika zopangidwa kuchokera ku thovu kapena zomatira, zomatira zokha.Zopangira nsalu zopangidwa ngati izi zimagwiritsidwa ntchito pafupifupi pafupifupi gawo lililonse la mafakitale.
Ubwino waukulu wogwiritsa ntchito ukadaulo wa laser pakudulira nsalu ndi m'mphepete osindikizidwa omwe amalepheretsa kuti zinthu zisawonongeke komanso kutsika.

Tsitsani Safari,
Ndi mawonekedwe ake osavuta komanso otsogola, Safari imakusoketsani mukamayangana pa intaneti ndikulolani kuti mukhale ndi intaneti yosangalatsa kwambiri mukamakhala otetezeka. Pulogalamuyi, yomwe Apple imakonda kwambiri kuthamanga komanso chitetezo, ikupitilizabe kupangidwira machitidwe a Windows.
Tsitsani Safari
Ndi zinthu zambiri monga kuchita mwachangu, mawonekedwe osavuta komanso mawonekedwe osavuta, kugwiritsa ntchito kosavuta, zokonda, kutsekereza pop, kusaka zinthu, kugwiritsa ntchito ma tabbed, kuthandizira kwa RSS, kudzaza mawonekedwe, malo osinthiratu, kuyenda kobisika komanso kwachinsinsi, komanso njira zotsogola zapamwamba Safari tsopano ndi njira ina yabwino kwa ogwiritsa ntchito Windows.
Safari 5, yomwe ili ndiukadaulo waukadaulo wa Nitro JavaScript, imapanga zotsatira za JavaScript nthawi 4,5 mwachangu kuposa mitundu yammbuyomu ya Safari, ndikupangitsa intaneti yanu kukhala yolimba kwambiri.
Pokhala ndi zinthu zambiri zatsopano monga HTML 5 yothandizira pa intaneti, zolemba zonse kuchokera pa mayeso a Acid 3, Apple Safari ndiwokonzeka kupanga intaneti yanu kukhala yotetezeka komanso mwachangu.
Pulogalamuyi ikuphatikizidwa pamndandanda wama pulogalamu aulere a Windows.

Chowdhury chiyambi. Bengali form of Chaudhary. Pezani Chowdhury chiyambi.
Dzina lomaliza Chowdhury lofala kwambiri Bangladesh. Pezani Chowdhury kutchulidwa dzina lakutchulidwa.
Mayina ogwirizana a Chowdhury m'mayiko ndi zinenero zosiyanasiyana: Chaudhari, Chaudhary, Chaudhri, Choudhary. Pezani Chowdhury muzinenero zina.
Mayina ambiri omwe ali ndi dzina Nidhi: Sharma, Chaudhary, Shrivas, Tutlani, Chuphal. Pezani Mndandanda wa mayina omwe ali ndi dzina Nidhi.
Mayina ambiri omwe ali nalo dzina Chowdhury: Nashrin, Akash, Atrika, Soumik, Anirvan. Pezani Maina omwe amapita ndi Chowdhury.
Kugwirizana kwa Nidhi ndi Chowdhury ndi 78%. Pezani Kugwirizana kwa Nidhi ndi Chowdhury.

Zakudya za Gelatin, chifukwa cha mtundu wawo komanso kuwonekera kwawo, zimakhala zosangalatsa nthawi zonse. Koma patchuthi ichi atha kukhala ochulukirapo zosangalatsa komanso zosangalatsa, kuphatikizapo chopatsa thanzi, chopepuka komanso chokoma kwa ana, ngati tiwonjezera zipatso zina ndikudulira gelatin m'njira yoyambirira. Tabwera ndi njira ziwiri.
Mmodzi wa iwo amakhala ikani zipatso mu galasi lodyera kuti mulawe mzidutswa. Timadzaza galasi ndi gelatin yamadzi ya kununkhira komwe timakonda ndikuyiyika mufiriji.
Zina, zodabwitsa kwambiri, zimapangidwa gwirani chidebe chachisanu silicone, yomwe ili yosangalatsa komanso njira zachibwana. Pabowo lililonse timayika chipatso ndikudzaza ndi gelatin. Tayika gelatin imadzipukutira m'madzi ndi fungo la vanila kuti imveke bwino ndipo chipatso chikuwoneka bwino. Timalola kuti kuzizire. Amawoneka ngati madzi oundana! Iwo ndi abwino kutumikiridwa mukamadya chakudya ndi zakumwa zosamwa mowa.

Sitima yapamtunda yochokera ku Mashhad kupita ku Yazd, yonyamula anthu 348 ndi ogwira nawo ntchito, yachoka kum'mawa kwa Iran, pafupifupi makilomita 50 (makilomita 31) kuchokera ku mzinda wachipululu wa Tabas, pafupi ndi siteshoni ya Mazino, lero.
Malinga ndi bungwe la Iran Red Crescent, anthu osachepera 21 ataya miyoyo yawo ndipo oposa 50 avulala kwambiri pangoziyi.
Ena mwa okwera sitima yapamtunda omwe anavulala anali pamavuto.
Magalimoto asanu ndi limodzi (11) mwa XNUMX amagalimoto a sitimayo adawonongeka kwambiri panjanjiyo.
Ma ambulansi khumi ndi ma helikoputala atatu adatumizidwa pamalo ochita ngozi pamodzi ndi opulumutsa ambiri.
Bungwe la Islamic Republic of Iran Railways lidapereka chikalata chonena kuti kusokonekera kunachitika pomwe sitimayo idawombana ndi chofukula.
Malinga ndi Bwanamkubwa wa Tabas, ogwira ntchito yopulumutsa anthu akufufuzabe magalimoto onse a sitima kuti apeze anthu ovulala kapena akufa.

Phwando la St. Martin la Tours lidzakhala pa 11. Anakondwerera mu November ndipo amatsatira mosiyanasiyana m'madera ambiri. Komabe, nkhani ya St. Martin ndi ntchito yotchuka - kugawana malaya - ali paliponse.
Nyimbo ndi mndandanda Sankt Martin Lied
Kwa ana, ulendo wa St. Martin ndi chifukwa chokondwerera pa zifukwa zosiyanasiyana. Kusamuka koteroku kumachitika m'mayiko ambiri a ku Ulaya, ngakhale kuti zinthu zing'onozing'ono zingakhale zosiyana m'deralo. Onse ali ofanana, komabe, kayendetsedwe ka nyali ndi nyali kupyolera mu malo okhala. Zingwezi zimagulidwa kapena zimagulitsidwa ndi sukulu komanso ana a sukulu okha.
Mtsinje uwu, anthu amatsagana ndi St. Martin wokwera. Ophunzirawo amaimba Martinslieder ndipo amatsagana ndi magulu.

Anev City ku Turkmenistan yasankhidwa kukhala Cultural Capital of the Turkic World yomwe ikubwera ya 2024, m'malo mwa Shusha City Azerbaijan.
Mu 2010, lingaliro la Cultural Capital of the Turkic World linakhazikitsidwa panthawi ya Istanbul International Organisation of Turkic Culture (TURKSOY) msonkhano. Malinga ndi chigamulochi, mzinda wochokera kumayiko a Turkic World umasankhidwa kukhala "likulu lachikhalidwe" pachaka.
Nduna ya Zachikhalidwe ku Azerbaijan, Adil Kerimli, adatenga nawo gawo pamwambowu ndikugogomezera zochitika zambiri zomwe zidachitika ku Shusha, zomwe zimakondwerera chikhalidwe cha Azerbaijan komanso dziko lonse la Turkic.
Adil Kerimli, Nduna Yoona za Chikhalidwe ku Azerbaijan, anatsindika za kukonzanso kwa malo akale komanso chikhalidwe cha anthu ku Shusha, pofuna kutsitsimulanso chikhalidwe chawo. Pakadali pano, Nduna Yowona Zachikhalidwe ku Turkmenistan, Atageldi Shamuradov, adawonetsa kuti ali ndi chiyembekezo chamgwirizano wachikhalidwe pakati pa mayiko a Turkic ndipo adayamika ntchito zotsogozedwa ndi TURKSOY.
Pamwambowu, opezekapo adawonera kanema wowonetsa Anev, yomwe idatsatiridwa ndi konsati yomwe idakhala ndi akatswiri aluso komanso otsogola ochokera ku Azerbaijan, Turkmenistan, ndi Uzbekistan.
Astana ku Kazakhstan adasankhidwa kukhala Cultural Capital of the Turkic World mu 2012, ndikutsatiridwa ndi Turkistan ku Kazakhstan, yomwe idasankhidwa mu 2017.

... (1207 chars skipped) ... 
ale mamembala kuti apange mgwirizano wapadziko lonse lapansi. Kuphatikiza mankhwala okhazikika komanso ochiritsira mkati mwa zokopa alendo zamankhwala sikunachitikepo.

Today Expedia ikupereka ndalama zatchuthi ku Zatoka, Ukraine, patsamba lake. Iwo tsopano ali m'mbuyo chifukwa Zatoka dzulo anawonongedwa ndi Russia.
Expedia imati: Mutha kusankha kuchokera pamaphukusi osiyanasiyana a Zatoka, monga galimoto yobwereka, ndege, ndi hotelo. Mukhozanso kusungitsa hotelo ndi ndege kapena galimoto yobwereka. Mukasungitsa malo, mutha kuwonjezera zinthu zosangalatsa monga zochitika ndi maulendo. Kaya maloto anu a Zatoka akuwoneka bwanji, khalani okonzeka kusunga!

oneka bwino a 5 miles (8 km) kuchokera pakati pa mzindawo.

Zatoka ndi malo okhala ngati matauni ku Karolino-Bugaz Hromada, Bilhorod-Dnistrovskyi Raion, kumwera chakumadzulo kwa Ukraine. Kukhazikikako ndi malo am'mphepete mwa nyanja. Kuphatikiza apo, Zatoka il

ld Tourism Network membala Mariana Oleskiv, Wapampando ku State Agency for Tourism Development, Ukraine. Wakhumudwa.

Russia ndi dziko la zigawenga.

Tower of Fantasy: osati Frigg yekha, chochitika chikubwera ndi galimoto komanso zojambula zambiri zaulere
- Ndemanga za News
Usiku womwewo Frigg's Banner idafika ku Tower of Fantasy, gulu lodziwika bwino lamasewera otseguka padziko lonse lapansi lalengeza za kuyamba kwanthawi kochepa ndi. mphotho zaulere.
Njira Yotsutsana, ili ndi dzina la chochitikacho, chidzatsegulidwa pamasewera usiku wa Ogasiti 31 mpaka Seputembara 1, 2022 ndipo zikhala pa intaneti mpaka Seputembara 14. Pamwambowu, osewera adzafunsidwa kuti amalize zochitika zingapo kuti apeze ndalama zokhazikika, mbewu ya nyenyezi, kuti mugwiritse ntchito mu shopu ya Road of Strife. Kupyolera mu ndalama - zidzakhala zotheka kupeza kuchuluka kwa 1 patsiku - zidzatheka kusinthanitsa zonse ziwiri. zida zowonjezera zida ce zofiira zofiira (magawo ofiira oti muwombere nawo mu mbendera yanthawi yake), komanso zigawo zachilendo mbalamerobotic flamingo yomwe imagwira ntchito ngati mayendedwe.

Tebulo La Khofi Prism ndi tebulo lomwe limafotokoza nkhani. Ziribe kanthu momwe mungayang'anire tebulo ili kuchokera pamenepo ndikuwonetseni zina zatsopano. Monga kuyala kotsutsa - tebulo ili limatenga mizere ya utoto, kutuluka mu bar imodzi ndikuwasintha kudutsa chimango chake. Mwa kuluka ndikukhotetsa mawonekedwe ake olongosola tebulo ili lisintha kuchokera pomwepo. Mitundu yosakanikirana ndi mitundu yosakanikirana imapanga mawonekedwe omwe amaphatikizika pamodzi kuti apange chathunthu. Prism ili ndi minimalism mu mawonekedwe ake ndi momwe imagwirira ntchito, ngakhale kuphatikiza ndi kupendekeka kwapang'onopang'ono mkati mwake, imawulula china chake chosayembekezeka komanso mwachiyembekezo chosamveka.
Dzina la polojekiti : Prism, Dzina laopanga : Maurie Novak, Dzina la kasitomala : MN Design.
Kupanga kwabwino kumeneku ndikopambana kwa mphotho ya kapangidwe mumapikisano opangira mapangidwe. Muyenera kuwona mawonekedwe opanga opambana mphoto kuti mupeze zinthu zina zambiri zatsopano, zaluso, zoyambira komanso zopangira.

Njira ya Gordon Bennett
Lolani Gordon Bennett Driving Route ikutengereni ulendo wosaiwalika kudutsa madera owoneka bwino aku Ireland ndikupita m'matawuni ndi midzi yokongola ya County Kildare mkatikati mwa Ireland.
Anathamangitsidwa koyamba mu 1903, lero njirayi imadutsa madera owoneka bwino kuyambira ku Athy mpaka ku Kilcullen, asanawoloke zigwa za Curragh kupita mtawuni ya Kildare ndipo pamapeto pake Monasterevin. Zizindikiro za msewu wa Gordon Bennett zimapangitsa Gordon Bennett Route kukhala njira yosavuta kutsatira kudzera kudera lokongola kwambiri ku Ireland komwe kumapereka chidziwitso chapadera pamiyoyo, mlengalenga komanso adrenalin kumbuyo kwa mpikisano wamagalimoto wakale womwe udawomba 166km (104- mile) dera. Khazikani mtima pansi, yambani kuyendetsa galimoto yanu ndikutsatira modekha mapazi a apainiya athu oyendetsa magalimoto omwe amakhala ndi nthawi yosangalala ndi zokopa alendo ambiri ku Ireland, midzi yakumidzi komanso malo osangalatsa panjira.
Phwando la Gordon Bennett limachitika mwezi uliwonse wa June ndi zochitika zambiri zokumbukira mpikisanowu kuphatikiza msonkhano wotsatira dera.
Za mapu ndi zina zambiri, Dinani apa.

Kukhazikitsa Ziboliboli Superegg ikuyimira kuchulukitsa kwa makapu amodzi a khofi kamodzi, komwe kumayimira kusavuta kwa anthu komanso momwe amathandizira chilengedwe. Ikuwoneka yokhazikika pamtunda, mawonekedwe a geometric superegg, monga wolemba masamu Gabriel Lame, amadzaza ndi makapisozi otayika a khofi omwe amatayika mwanjira zabwino. Zochitika mu visceral zimapenyetsa wowonera kuchokera kuzonse ndi mtunda. Zapamwamba zopitilira 3000 adazipeza kudzera pakuyitanitsa kuchitapo kanthu pazanema komanso anthu wamba. Superegg imalola wopenyerera kuti awononge zinyalala ndikulimbikitsa njira zatsopano zobwezeretsanso.
Dzina la polojekiti : Superegg, Dzina laopanga : Jaco Roeloffs, Dzina la kasitomala : Jaco Roeloffs.

CHIPANI CHA A SISTERE CHA M.M.M CHAYAMIKILIDWA KAMBA KA NTCHITO ZAKE MU ARKIDAYOSIZI YAKATOLIKA YA LILONGWE
Wolemba ndi Sam Kalimba
Arkidayosizi ya Lilongwe yayamikira ndi kulimbikitsa a sistere a chipani cha Missionaries of Mary Mediatrix (M.M.M) kamba ka utumiki wawo womwe ati akuwugwira modziyiwala mu Arkidayosiziyi.
Arkiepisikopi wa Arkidayosiziyi George Desmond Tambala ndiwo ayankhula izi pa mbuyo pa mwambo wa Misa ya malumbiro oyamba a Sr. Apronia Mahowe ndi Sr. Stella Mkwezalamba a chipanichi ku parish ya Kaggwa Loweruka pa 27 January 2024.
Ambuye Tambala anati iwo akudziwa bwino mâ€™mene amayi achipanichi akugwirira ntchito zothandiza anthu pachipatala cha Mlare.
Mâ€™mau ake, bambo mfumu wa parish ya Andrea Kaggwa Woyera Monsignor Patrick Thawale wayamikira ntchito zomwe amayiwa akugwira pa parishiyi monga kuphunzitsa ana pa sukulu ya Wisdom Center komanso kuthandizira pa misa za ku ma outstation.
Mayi mkulu wa chipani cha Missionaries of Mary Mediatrix Sr. Mercedes Arbesu ochokera ku likulu la chipanichi ku Spain anali nawo pa mwambowu.
